snippet.textDisplay:
Mohabbat ke liye shukriya ! 

The first song that stayed with me in its entirety from Coke Studio was “Aik Alif” It was released in June of 2009 lines “jo mann ke Dariya mei doube / kaisi naaiya kya manjdaar” 

Kissi ne nahi kaha doube tou Sahi. Naaiya Bhi tum khud manjdhar Bhi tum khud. Aur maanjhii Bhi tum khud. 

In between the belief in yourself and others believing in you. You find your self. Some lift you & some have their own fights to fight. 

Hazaroun baar jalne pe mili hai raushni Tuj ko
Kare kyun gair ab ye tai ki kitna jagmagaana hai 

Nahi hai Haq usse iska kahaan tha woh Andheroun mei 
Siyah hai rang Tera raushni mei jagmagaata hai
-
Tumhein maloom nahi tum Kaun ho 
Tum qaid nahi jo ijazat lo 

-
Alif
